org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.sql
Class AeSQLDatabaseType

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.sql.AeSQLObject
      org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.sql.AeSQLDatabaseType
public class AeSQLDatabaseType
extends AeSQLObject

Implements a database type lookup from the database. The database has been configured with a value for DatabaseType in the meta info table. This row will contain the type of the database, for example: mysql, db2, sqlserver, or oracle. The application checks this value against the value found in the engine configuration as an extra configuration check.
